graph TD
    A[Client: POST /adventures] --> B[Backend: Create Placeholder Adventure & Avatar]
    B --> C[Backend: Start Background Generation Task]
    CAT[(Style & Tone Catalog)] -.-> D
    C --> D[WorldGenerator: generate_world]
    D --> E[LLM: Analyze Story Idea]
    E --> F[Generate WorldManifesto<br/>(Scenes, Exits, NPCs, Objects, Protagonist)]
    F --> G[WorldGenerator: apply_manifest]
    G --> H[Clear Existing World Data]
    H --> I[Sync Protagonist to Avatar]
    I --> J[Generate Protagonist Image (if enabled)]
    J --> K[Iterate & Generate Scenes]
    K --> L[Generate Scene Images (if enabled)]
    L --> M[Iterate & Generate NPCs]
    M --> N[Generate NPC Images (if enabled)]
    N --> O[Iterate & Generate Objects]
    O --> P[Generate Object Images (if enabled)]
    P --> Q[Initialize Quests & Awards]
    Q --> R[Save Exits to DB]
    R --> S[Update Adventure Status: Ready]
    S --> T[End Background Task]
